author: Paula Benson
text: Just gave to @CatsProtection for Betty White's 100th birthday. She was an avid supporter of animal charities & so in celebration of this, it was suggested that a donation to a charity would be a nice idea. I gave £5, not much but it will help feed a cat. Go do it too if you can.

author: Paula Benson
text: Just watched the new @russellhoward special on Netflix and it was really good. What was a surprise was the documentary afterwards showing the span of a 20 year+ career and just how steadfast someone can be to get on stage & do what they do best. Absolutely fantastic, seriously.

text: Well, I finished it in one sitting. That was 8 episodes in a row. This is why people who say things like "We need to split films up into parts, nobody will just sit and watch it all at once!" is a load of rubbish. Yes, yes we will. Maybe ad a few ad breaks for loo and drinks.

author: Paula Benson
text: Oh, I just got my replacement card from @TSB and oh, it's smooth. Very simple. Different from the old look but I like it. A big plus also is the number stayed the same. It's always annoying when you have to change all the things it's attached too. #itsthelittlethings #nice

author: Paula Benson
text: Gosh, the new #CSIVegas trailer just gave me shivers. I cannot wait for it. I hope we see more of the old crew return even if it's just in flash backs or small scenes. A catch up of what everyone else has been up to these last six years. #excited
